          span.colortext
              | #{data.date}
      h1(style='color: darkmagenta') Departure time: &nbsp
          span.colortext
              |7:15 AM
      h1(style='color: darkmagenta') Travel time: &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp
          span.colortext
              |2hr 15min
      h1(style='color: darkmagenta') Arrival time: &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp
          span.colortext
              |9:30 AM





